  "detailed_description": "Cool and simple samurai action game!<br><br>Kill your enemies with stylish swordsmanship.<br>Let's kill 100!<br><br>Controls:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Move<br></li><li>Slash / Iai<br></li><li>Avoid (Stamina is continuously consumed while inputting)<br></li><li>Dash<br></li><li>Sheath a sword</li></ul><br>Rules:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Clear: 100 kills<br></li><li>GameOver: Fail to avoid the enemy's attack twice.</li></ul><br>Stages:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Summer: Tutorial<br></li><li>Fall: Samurai enemies<br></li><li>Winter: Ninja enemies<br></li><li>Spring: Samurai and Ninja enemies</li></ul><br>Costumes:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>8 costumes</li></ul>",
